updates.title: VAICOM PRO Community Edition for DCS World
updates.releasenotes: Clarification of hooking on PTT Tab on Vaicom UI, more bug fixes due to typos, completed Afghanistan Chatter theme, Adds F-5E Flaming Cliffs version (WIP) still crash DCS if Vaicom running on slotting, Adds community Super Hornet mod F/A-18E/F and EA-18G.
